I too wanna make a difference.

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:42.160
Let's pray, Father, we do love you

00:38:42.160 --> 00:38:44.040
and we thank you so much for loving us.

00:38:44.040 --> 00:38:47.340
We thank you for the privilege of being able to gather.

00:38:47.340 --> 00:38:49.720
We thank you for the freedom.

00:38:49.720 --> 00:38:51.880
We thank you for the word of God.

00:38:51.880 --> 00:38:54.680
We thank you for the example of Jehoshaphat.

00:38:54.680 --> 00:38:57.560
And Lord, I pray that today you would help each one of us

00:38:57.560 --> 00:39:02.440
here to examine our own lives,

00:39:02.440 --> 00:39:06.080
to not only look at the life of Jehoshaphat

00:39:06.120 --> 00:39:09.040
and to be thankful or to be encouraged

00:39:09.040 --> 00:39:11.180
by the actions that she took,

00:39:11.180 --> 00:39:14.200
but God, that you would help each one of us

00:39:14.200 --> 00:39:18.640
to take initiative, to be intentional,

00:39:19.560 --> 00:39:21.760
and then to have that influence.

00:39:23.040 --> 00:39:25.360
Oftentimes we'd say we want the influence,

00:39:25.360 --> 00:39:28.360
but we understand the path that it comes through

00:39:28.360 --> 00:39:31.920
as we examine this particular portion of scripture.

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:33.360
And God, I pray that you would help

00:39:33.360 --> 00:39:35.320
each one of us this morning.

00:39:35.320 --> 00:39:38.080
God, if there's one here that's not saved,

00:39:38.080 --> 00:39:38.920
if they were to die today,

00:39:38.920 --> 00:39:41.560
they're not 100% sure they'd go to heaven.

00:39:41.560 --> 00:39:42.960
I pray that you would,

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:44.400
Lord, we didn't deal with the gospel

00:39:44.400 --> 00:39:45.600
specifically this morning,

00:39:45.600 --> 00:39:48.360
but God, we sang about the blood.

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:50.880
Maybe there's one that needs to come

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:53.240
and we could take a Bible and we could show them

00:39:53.240 --> 00:39:56.320
how they could know for sure that heaven is their home.

00:39:56.320 --> 00:39:57.820
I pray, God, that you'd move and work

00:39:57.820 --> 00:40:00.360
in their hearts and lives as only you can.

00:40:00.360 --> 00:40:01.360
Again, we thank you.

00:40:01.360 --> 00:40:03.020
for the opportunity, I pray that you'd bless

00:40:03.020 --> 00:40:05.020
during the time of invitation,

00:40:05.020 --> 00:40:06.220
that every decision that's made

00:40:06.220 --> 00:40:07.660
would bring honor and glory to thy name,

00:40:07.660 --> 00:40:09.460
for it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:40:09.460 --> 00:40:10.300
Would you stand with me?

00:40:10.300 --> 00:40:11.420
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:40:11.420 --> 00:40:13.060
We have an opportunity at the end of our services

00:40:13.060 --> 00:40:14.820
to have a time of invitation.

